4
00:00:20,380 --> 00:00:26,436
♪ Hold me tight,
let the darkness drown me ♪

5
00:00:26,460 --> 00:00:33,560
♪ Even one second of truth is enough
to lose myself in it ♪

6
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:40,296
♪ Whether you're light or a lie,
I can't pull myself away ♪

7
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:46,760
♪ In this game,
truth or lie no longer matters ♪

8
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:51,976
[Queen of Darkness]

9
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:54,000
[Episode 2]

10
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:14,656
If we remove the chip
from the flash drive,

11
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:16,096
we can crack the data inside.

12
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:18,040
But this kind of drive
has an anti-tamper system,

13
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:19,880
if we force the chip out,

14
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:22,360
all the data will erase itself.

15
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,040
Ye Hong is already dead.

16
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,320
The only one who might know the password

17
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:33,480
is probably his daughter, Ye Ying.

18
00:01:36,320 --> 00:01:37,320
Inspector,

19
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:38,177
this month,

20
00:01:38,201 --> 00:01:40,256
we've received three reports
about Song Pa's gang crimes.

21
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:43,760
And letters accusing him of murdering
An Yuan, ex-chairman of Longxing Group.

22
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,456
I'll handle this case personally.

23
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:47,040
Keep tracing that person's whereabouts.

24
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,456
You were drugged and confused back then.

25
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:51,216
The clues you gave were quite vague.

26
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,776
And that person is overseas.

27
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,560
It's hard to find the girl who saved you.

28
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:01,720
Inspector.

29
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,080
It was me who called the police.

30
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:11,337
Inspector.

31
00:02:11,361 --> 00:02:12,376
I called the police.

32
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,456
Is there a problem with that?

33
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,520
You...

34
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,480
Don't recognize me?

35
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,240
Xiao.

36
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:23,920
Uncle.

37
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:26,920
What brings you here?

38
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,240
Xiao.

39
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:41,480
Come on.

40
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,720
Have some tea.

41
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,960
Thanks, Uncle.

42
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,800
You're too kind.

43
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:51,280
You're the police inspector.

44
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:54,440
That's a position
everyone dreams of connecting with.

45
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,280
For me to serve you tea,

46
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,680
it's my honor.

47
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:00,040
Xiao.

48
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:02,960
These are the shares
your father left in the group.

49
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:04,177
From now on,

50
00:03:04,201 --> 00:03:05,840
you'll keep them yourself.

51
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,216
To be honest with you,

52
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,296
the company right now

53
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:10,976
has attracted some unwanted attention.

54
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,296
We run many businesses.

55
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:15,000
Dealing with all sorts of people
is unavoidable.

56
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,497
But someone

57
00:03:16,521 --> 00:03:17,816
took advantage of that detail,

58
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,936
and reported the group.

59
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,320
Saying we're linked to some gangs.

60
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,456
Recently,

61
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:24,136
the authorities have been
cracking down hard on gang crimes.

62
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,800
This matter could turn big or stay small.

63
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,016
Some groups

64
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,640
have already been fined into bankruptcy.

65
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,817
Xiao.

66
00:03:29,841 --> 00:03:30,936
You're the inspector here.

67
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:31,737
This issue

68
00:03:31,761 --> 00:03:33,080
only you can resolve it.

69
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:34,976
Longxing Group

70
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,536
was also built from
your father's hard work.

71
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,720
Just do something.

72
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:41,696
You took over the company
from An Yuan back then.

73
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:43,896
And you treated Huo family quite well.

74
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:44,737
Don't worry.

75
00:03:44,761 --> 00:03:47,000
I won't let my own interests be harmed.

76
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:50,320
But to resolve this matter completely,

77
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,496
we have to find whoever reported it.

78
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,400
The group's transactions
are confidential.

79
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,640
Maybe the problem lies in this house.

80
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:02,760
How about this.

81
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,840
I'll stay here for a few days.

82
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,736
Let's see if we can find any clues.

83
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:07,760
Sure.

84
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:09,200
Xiao.

85
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,896
You're willing to help.

86
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:12,120
That really puts me at ease.

87
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:31,320
I heard you're Ti Cha's wife,

88
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:32,960
An Ning.

89
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:42,416
He's pretty close with Song Pa.

90
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:44,240
No matter who I really am,

91
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:47,160
I'll just play An Ning for now.

92
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,520
Right.

93
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,256
I lost my memory.

94
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,800
I don't remember anything from before.

95
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:02,200
Someone who doesn't even know
who she is,

96
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:04,960
yet reports that
someone here is trying to hurt you.

97
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:10,016
Before my dad died,

98
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,816
he gave me shares of Longxing Group.

99
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:13,880
The Song family wanted to harm me
to get the shares.

100
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:24,280
Since you lost your memory,

101
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,376
how do you know these things?

102
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:28,160
Let go of me.

103
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,137
I can prove it.

104
00:05:32,161 --> 00:05:33,441
There are records on the tablet.

105
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,536
I just lost my memory.

106
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,640
It doesn't mean I'm stupid.

107
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:39,280
I can still read the records on the tablet.

108
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,800
This is a photo of me and my dad.

109
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,000
He's not Ye Hong.

110
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,120
Since you've lost your memory,

111
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,760
maybe,

112
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:10,080
there's been a misunderstanding
between you and the Song family.

113
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,160
I can prove what I'm saying.

114
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,816
But you have to promise me,

115
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:17,600
you won't twist the law
for personal reasons.

116
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,880
It's not your place to question me.

117
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:24,360
Until your claims are verified,

118
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,720
I'll keep an eye on you myself.

119
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:34,056
I don't even know what went wrong

120
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:35,576
to make An Ning misunderstand me.

121
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,880
She actually called the police.

122
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,736
Luckily, the one who came was Xiao.

123
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:42,720
Otherwise, people might think
I'm a terrible mother-in-law.

124
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,616
An Ning.

125
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,536
You're hurt and still weak.

126
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:49,216
I asked the kitchen to make your
favorite dumplings.

127
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:51,216
No matter how much resentment you have,

128
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,576
just take it out on me.

129
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,600
Please don't blame anyone else at home.

130
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:56,840
An Ning.

131
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,616
You were the one
causing trouble for no reason.

132
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:00,736
Your mother-in-law was kind enough
not to hold it against you.

133
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:01,360
Well,

134
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:03,376
eat the dumplings now.

135
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:05,960
Then we'll forget about that false
police call.

136
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,576
That's quite a blessing.

137
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,296
Why are you still hesitating?

138
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,176
My mom told you to eat,

139
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,097
so just eat!

140
00:07:16,121 --> 00:07:17,440
Don't be ungrateful.

141
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,096
That car crash didn't kill you.

142
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,736
Then I'll poison you instead.

143
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:22,736
Huo Xiao is on our side.

144
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:24,496
We'll have an inspector to back us up.

145
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:27,200
You'll die as silently as your father did.

146
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,600
Steward.

147
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:33,936
Looks like An Ning doesn't know
how to eat these dumplings.

148
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:35,120
Give her a hand.

149
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,736
Since it's a blessing,

150
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:54,000
I'll let you have it.

151
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,560
Madam.

152
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,000
You... you...

153
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:06,416
Such a clumsy trick.

154
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:08,416
Can't tell if you're bold,

155
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:10,400
or just foolish.

156
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:20,720
An Ning.

157
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:22,256
You're still recovering from that accident.

158
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:23,936
You need more rest.

159
00:08:23,960 --> 00:08:26,280
Have a cup of ginseng tea
to rebuild your strength.

160
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,280
I don't want it now.

161
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:31,120
Come on, drink it, it's good for you.

162
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:48,896
You're the well-known steward
of the Song family.

163
00:08:48,920 --> 00:08:51,320
How dare An Ning force you
to eat dumplings?

164
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,200
She clearly doesn't respect you at all.

165
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,816
She's just a tool

166
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,600
for Master Song Pa
and Young Master Ti Cha.

167
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,640
That woman's not worth a dime.

168
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:02,000
Even if I kill her,

169
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:04,080
no one would even bother about her.

170
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:07,840
Killing her would be
letting her off too easy.

171
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:10,360
As long as you get something on her,

172
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:12,480
she'll be under your control from then on.

173
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,760
This drug

174
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:18,240
is really strong.

175
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:23,016
Just wait until she falls for your charm.

176
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:24,520
Then take a video.

177
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:26,200
From then on,

178
00:09:26,880 --> 00:09:28,960
she'll do whatever you say.

179
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,480
I...

180
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:53,656
Dare to fool around?

181
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:54,896
Dare to sneak around!

182
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:55,920
Homewrecker!

183
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:58,496
How dare you cuckold me!

184
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,520
Ti Cha.

185
00:10:02,880 --> 00:10:03,960
Why are you here?

186
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,377
Then where should I be?

187
00:10:05,401 --> 00:10:06,680
- No.
- Here?

188
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:13,680
Steward?

189
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,000
Fang Yao?

190
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:17,536
Why are you both in my room?

191
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:18,560
And...

192
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:19,840
In this state?

193
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:21,720
Y... Young Master, please let me explain.

194
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:24,056
You dared to lay hands on my woman!

195
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:24,456
I...

196
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,480
Young Master.

197
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,440
Young Master!

198
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,640
It's time for my medicine.

199
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:44,680
Yao.

200
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:46,096
It's in the cabinet behind you.

201
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,120
Help me get the medicine.

202
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:48,960
Mm.

203
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,520
Master, Madam.

204
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:01,920
It wasn't me.

205
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:03,976
Inspector Huo.

206
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,336
I swear it really wasn't me.

207
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:07,840
I know you couldn't have done this alone.

208
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:11,400
Just tell me who's working with you.

209
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:14,040
I can ask Young Master Ti Cha
to spare you.

210
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,017
Inspector Huo

211
00:11:15,041 --> 00:11:16,200
will stand up for you too.

212
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,480
An Ning.

213
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:19,280
We have shown you endless patience.

214
00:11:19,281 --> 00:11:39,575
Officail Website : kissasian.be  Translate by =Qari= @Team Viki

215
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,776
Why would you sink to something
so despicable?

216
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:23,096
You even tried to
harm your closest friend!

217
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:25,480
The Song family won't
tolerate a ruthless heart.

218
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,216
If you act up again,

219
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:28,336
don't blame us for being unforgiving!

220
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:28,977
Dad.

221
00:11:29,001 --> 00:11:30,416
Hurry and get Inspector Huo over here.

222
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,576
Send her straight to jail.

223
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,456
Otherwise,
she'll drag Song family down with her.

224
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,457
Exactly.

225
00:11:34,481 --> 00:11:36,536
Call our lawyer to let her
sign the share transfer agreement.

226
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:38,296
She must pay for what she's done.

227
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,440
Have you all finished?

228
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:42,977
Inspector Huo.

229
00:11:43,001 --> 00:11:45,040
Isn't it time the steward
had his turn to speak?

230
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:58,280
It was Fang Yao.

231
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,896
Fang Yao tried to drug An Ning.

232
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:02,720
And frame her for being unfaithful.

233
00:12:03,160 --> 00:12:04,576
Luckily, karma stepped in.

234
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:06,160
She ended up facing her own punishment.

235
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,896
I heard Song Pa intends to set you up

236
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:12,656
with a wealthy businessman's widow.

237
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:14,520
If your scandal gets out,

238
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,936
that rich lady
may not fancy you anymore.

239
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:17,360
You...

240
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:18,560
Shut up.

241
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:20,736
Making me shut up is possible.

242
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:23,520
You need to show some sincerity.

243
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,640
You're slandering me!

244
00:12:28,280 --> 00:12:28,976
Ti Cha.

245
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:29,657
Believe me.

246
00:12:29,681 --> 00:12:30,800
I really didn't do it.

247
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,816
It's... it's An Ning.

248
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:35,096
An Ning must have bribed the steward
to frame me.

249
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,560
To catch a thief, you need evidence.

250
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:37,577
If it was you who did it,

251
00:12:37,601 --> 00:12:38,841
we'll know after a body search.

252
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:40,216
Right?

253
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:41,240
Inspector Huo.

254
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,080
Don't come over.

255
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:46,737
You...

256
00:12:46,761 --> 00:12:48,040
You've got no proof.

257
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:00,400
Inspector Huo.

258
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:03,136
I told you someone here
wants to harm me.

259
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:04,240
This is the evidence.

260
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:10,960
Get up.

261
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:25,897
An Ning.

262
00:13:25,921 --> 00:13:26,976
It's all a misunderstanding.

263
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:29,176
We've been best friends for years.

264
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,200
Best friends?

265
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:32,376
Would a best friend seduce her husband?

266
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:33,896
Or side with outsiders to bully her?

267
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:35,680
Or scheme to ruin her forever?

268
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:37,256
No way.

269
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:37,897
How could you...

270
00:13:37,921 --> 00:13:39,016
How?

271
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:40,256
How come I'm not as stupid as before?

272
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:40,777
Right?

273
00:13:40,801 --> 00:13:42,736
If it weren't for our old friendship,

274
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:44,496
you wouldn't have just been kicked out
of the Song family.

275
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:45,576
If you're smart,

276
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:46,640
then get out of here.

277
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:48,200
If I see you again,

278
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:50,000
you won't be so lucky next time.

279
00:13:59,920 --> 00:14:01,096
Useless fool!

280
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,576
You can't even handle
such a simple matter.

281
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,096
Let that skank An Ning come back alive.

282
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:05,856
And causing so much trouble.

283
00:14:05,880 --> 00:14:07,216
Not even a car crash could take her out.

284
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,816
What else can I do?

285
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:09,536
Besides,

286
00:14:09,560 --> 00:14:10,176
didn't you also...

287
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,200
Just shut up!

288
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:20,616
Right now.

289
00:14:20,640 --> 00:14:21,497
Immediately.

290
00:14:21,521 --> 00:14:22,720
Teach An Ning a lesson!

291
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:32,136
Your daughter-in-law suffered
severe head trauma,

292
00:14:32,160 --> 00:14:33,696
which caused retrograde amnesia.

293
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:35,256
But familiar people and places

294
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:36,680
could help trigger your memory.

295
00:15:23,240 --> 00:15:26,390
♪ Mist coils around the sleeping forest ♪

296
00:15:26,860 --> 00:15:30,040
♪ Memories scattered
through cracks of darkness ♪

297
00:15:30,410 --> 00:15:33,890
♪ How to escape this real-feeling dream ♪

298
00:15:37,430 --> 00:15:40,690
♪ Lies reflect in water's gleam ♪

299
00:15:40,920 --> 00:15:44,250
♪ Traces of existence
can never be erased ♪

300
00:15:44,540 --> 00:15:47,820
♪ How to find the self I can't reclaim ♪

301
00:15:50,130 --> 00:15:57,200
♪ Fly away, hear she says ♪

302
00:15:57,280 --> 00:16:01,236
♪ She'll fly out from
thorns of woven lies ♪

303
00:16:01,260 --> 00:16:04,836
♪ Pierce the fog,
shatter this dream tonight ♪

304
00:16:04,860 --> 00:16:07,796
♪ Burn like fire ♪

305
00:16:07,820 --> 00:16:11,230
♪ Just burn like fire ♪

306
00:16:11,450 --> 00:16:15,330
♪ The maze in the abyss starts to clear ♪

307
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:18,056
♪ Yet night keep on whispering ♪

308
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:21,220
♪ Surrender to fate,
no clear direction ahead ♪

309
00:16:21,510 --> 00:16:25,010
♪ She will rise as the dawn
that breaks the darkness ♪

310
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:31,540
♪ Never slowing down,
for tomorrow cannot be stopped ♪

311
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:35,516
♪ Surrender to love and find the way ♪

312
00:16:35,540 --> 00:16:39,060
♪ Even if fate tries to forget her ♪

313
00:16:39,280 --> 00:16:45,810
♪ Never despair,
for the heart burns with endless light ♪

314
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:48,070
♪ Waiting for dawn ♪

